description: Agnes Joubert is a secondary character in the series "Tiger & Bunny". She is the talented producer of Hero TV, who is always doing her best to give the channel the highest ratings possible. The orders Agnes ensues to command the Heroes usually have the objective of increasing the ratings, but she also tries to keep their safety. She is a woman with nerves of steel, and can be considered an elder sister figure to the Heroes.
name: Agnes Joubert
